highlights.text: “Chhore NCR Aale” by Paradox and MC SQUARE is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Jaipur, up 30 spots at #60.
“Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Jaipur the longest, at 58 weeks straight.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Jaipur. “Kesariya” is the highest at #3.
“Baazigar” by DIVINE and Armani White is the highest new entry on Top Songs Jaipur at #59.
